&lt;p&gt;생성일: 2021년 8월 11일 오후 12:49
태그: basic&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;판다스(Pandas)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;판다스(Pandas)는 파이썬 데이터 처리를 위한 라이브러리로써 데이터 분석 작업에서 필수적인 라이브러리다.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;판다스는 총 세가지의 데이터 구조를 사용한다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;시리즈(Series)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;데이터프레임(Dataframe)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;패널(Panel)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;시리즈(Series)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;시리즈 클래스는 1차원 배열의 값(values)에 각 값에 대응되는 인덱스(index)를 부여할 수 있는 구조를 갖는다.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;python&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-python&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-python&quot;&gt;sr &lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; pd&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;Series&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;17000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;18000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;1000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;5000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
       index&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;피자&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;치킨&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;콜라&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&quot;맥주&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;token keyword&quot;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;sr&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

피자    &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;17000&lt;/span&gt;
치킨    &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;18000&lt;/span&gt;
콜라     &lt;span class=&quot;token number&quot;&gt;1000&lt;/span&gt;
